1 Peter 2:17 (NIV)\
17\'a0Show proper respect to everyone, love the family of believers, fear God, honor the emperor.\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}There are two tensions I think Peter is addressing when he writes that scripture that way.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf3 {\listtext	\'95	}Government is to 
\f0\b BLINDLY
\f1\b0  
\f0\b ACCEPT
\f1\b0  or 
\f0\b REBELLIOUSLY
\f1\b0  
\f0\b REJECT
\f1\b0 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li1440\fi-1440\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}The first is the tension to vilify the emperor and use who he is as an excuse to do say or act in terrible ways toward him or anyone who supports him...after all...this guy was the worst. I know you think Trump or Biden is bad...I promise the emperor was worse.\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li2160\fi-2160\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Peter starts out saying we should respect everyone and then ends it with this almost...and that includes the emperor...\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Menaing there are no exceptions...\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li1440\fi-1440\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}But the second is just as important and maybe a little more subtle...\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li2160\fi-2160\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}The first 3 things Peter tells us to do is to repect everyone...makes sense...love the famiy of believers...there is a progression of sorts here of importance...then to fear God. Then...as if to correct any future potential wrong way of understanding the role of leadership...Peter say to honor the emperor...\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}I think this might be a sublt way of putting God next to the emperor and reminding them...we fear...we honor the emporer...becuase the emperoro is NOT GOD.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}Now I know what you thinking...we don't have to worry about worshiping our president or vilifying him...we're in Amercia in 2025...we would never do either of those two things!\
{\listtext	\'95	}(fades away)\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
