\f3\b \cf5 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Thomas Jeffersona and his Bible \

\fs31\fsmilli15585 Jefferson\'92s Beliefs
\f4\b0 :\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\qc\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}Jefferson admired Jesus\'92 moral teachings but struggled with the supernatural elements of the Bible, such as miracles, the resurrection, and the divinity of Christ.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}He considered himself a deist, believing in a Creator but rejecting much of traditional Christian theology.
\f3\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \
\pard\tx560\tx1120\pardeftab720\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa240\qc\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf5 {\listtext	1	}The Jefferson Bible
\f4\b0 :\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\qc\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}In 1820, Jefferson took two physical copies of the New Testament in Greek, Latin, French, and English and began cutting out passages he deemed morally valuable or historically credible.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}He excluded:\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\qc\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl2\cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}Miracles, such as Jesus walking on water or turning water into wine.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}References to Jesus\'92 divinity and resurrection.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}Events that Jefferson considered supernatural or inconsistent with reason.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\qc\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}What remained were sections focused on Jesus\'92 ethical teachings, such as the Sermon on the Mount and parables.\
\pard\tx560\tx1120\pardeftab720\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b \cf5 \
The Result
\f4\b0 :\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\qc\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1\cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}The result was a much shorter version of the Gospels that Jefferson viewed as a manual for moral living rather than a record of divine revelation.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}He reportedly kept this book for personal study and reflection but did not intend for it to replace the Bible in a broader religious sense.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs36\fsmilli18182 \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \
\
\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\slleading24\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
